<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Subscription Expired</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 700px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
        <div style="border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            <h2 style="color: #00466a;">Xuthority</h2>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em;">
            Hi <%= userName %>,
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1.1em; color: #dc3545; font-weight: bold;">
            ‚è∞ Your Subscription Has Expired
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            Your <strong><%= planName %></strong> subscription expired on <strong><%= expiredDate %></strong>. We wanted to let you know about the changes to your account and how to restore your premium access.
        </p>

        <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #dc3545; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-weight: bold; color: #721c24;">
                üìã Account Status:
            </p>
            <div style="color: #666;">
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Previous Plan:</strong> <%= planName %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Expired On:</strong> <%= expiredDate %></p>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Current Status:</strong> Free Plan</p>
                <% if (reasonForExpiry) { %>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;"><strong>Reason:</strong> <%= reasonForExpiry %></p>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #856404; font-weight: bold;">
                üîÑ What's Changed
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #856404;">
                Your account has been automatically moved to our free plan. You can still access basic features, but some premium functionality may no longer be available.
            </p>
        </div>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            <strong>What you still have access to:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 1em; color: #666; margin-left: 20px;">
            <li>Basic dashboard and account management</li>
            <li>Limited product listings</li>
            <li>Community access</li>
            <li>Basic customer support</li>
        </ul>

        <p style="font-size: 1em;">
            <strong>What you're missing out on:</strong>
        </p>
        <ul style="font-size: 1em; color: #dc3545; margin-left: 20px;">
            <% if (lostFeatures && lostFeatures.length > 0) { %>
                <% lostFeatures.forEach(function(feature) { %>
                <li><%= feature %></li>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
            <li>Enhanced branding and profile customization</li>
            <li>Advanced analytics and insights</li>
            <li>Priority customer support</li>
            <li>Unlimited product listings</li>
            <li>Lead generation tools</li>
            <% } %>
        </ul>

        <div style="background-color: #d4edda; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724; font-weight: bold;">
                üöÄ Ready to Upgrade Again?
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #155724;">
                Reactivate your subscription today and regain access to all premium features instantly! Choose from our flexible plans designed to help your business grow.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a href="<%= upgradeUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #28a745; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 10px;">
                Reactivate Subscription
            </a>
            <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" 
               style="background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold;">
                View Dashboard
            </a>
        </div>

        <% if (specialOffer) { %>
        <div style="background-color: #e7f3ff; border-left: 4px solid #007bff; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #004085; font-weight: bold;">
                üéÅ Special Offer Just for You!
            </p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #004085;">
                <%= specialOffer %>
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            <strong>Need Help?</strong><br>
            If you're experiencing payment issues or have questions about reactivating your subscription, our support team is here to help. Contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>" style="color: #00466a;"><%= supportEmail %></a>.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            We value having you as part of our community and hope to continue serving your business needs.
        </p>

        <p style="font-size: 0.9em; color: #888;">
            Best regards,<br>
            The Xuthority Team
        </p>

        <div style="border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; padding-top: 10px; font-size: 0.8em; color: #aaa;">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p><%= companyAddress %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 